## 3. Personas

| Persona | Reads | Writes | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Engineer** | Dashboards for their team | nothing | Daily-standup user |
| **Team lead** | Per-team slice; per-initiative slice | refresh trigger | Weekly retro user |
| **Org admin** | All contracts, all dashboards | contract YAML, token rotation | Quarterly + on-change user |
| **LLM agent** | JSON API read endpoints | nothing in v1 | Triggered by chat tools |
| **Engineering exec** | Cross-team rollups | nothing | Monthly review user |

The contract editor is the only frequent admin write path. Token rotation
and contract changes are infrequent but high-trust.

